name: ONE-OFF EYE.W.E Triangle Sweater - UK LARGE
description:
ONE-OFF, hand printed, hand dyed EYE.W.E TRIANGLE Sweater. UK SIZE LARGE

Get in the mood for christmas with this one-off sparkly print sweater. This is one of a kind so grab it before it's gone!
As each sweater is individually hand dyed, no sweater is exactly the same as the next! 

PLEASE NOTE: ALL sweater are hand-dyed, though each sweater has been washed, it is important to wash INDIVIDUALLY and preferably BY HAND. Please turn sweater inside out to iron, do not iron directly onto the print. 

Some sweater may have a starchy feel to them, this is due to the way the sweater is dyed, this will disappear after a few wears/washes
